license: CC-BY-4.0
keywords:
  - agent colony
  - multi-agent systems
  - agent architecture
  - agent mirror
  - pattern language
  - autonomous agents
  - AI governance
abstract: >
  A universal architectural pattern for self-governing ecosystems of autonomous
  AI agents that persist beyond projects, evolve across technology generations,
  and coexist with human organisations through defined boundaries. The work
  includes seven principles (including accessibility through abstraction and
  the audience-lens model), the Agent Mirror identity standard, and analysis
  of six gaps in current standards.
